mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "Discovery - Department for New Square Dancers", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Vox Saltator: The Square Dancer Speaks Up", "Homes for Square Dancing - Sacramento's New Dance Studio", "Nine in a Square", "Teaching Sequence for TV Show", "Ladies on the Square", "Style Series: Alamo Style Allemande", "Style Series: Nine Pin (A Square Mixer)", "Overseas Dateline", "Round the Outside Ring", "Workshop", "Caller of the Month: Margaret Hough", "Paging the Roundancers: Alvin & Mildred Boutillier", and "Experimental Lab - Curl Thru".
